  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1766915713}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 3089b53a39858db4d8673bfadcdc12d5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogBox: {fileID: 1762141775}
  dialogText: {fileID: 1300943634}
  speakerNameText: {fileID: 121795798}
  portraitImage: {fileID: 1288517481}
  portraitFrame: {fileID: 1172073840}
  dark: {fileID: 365560361}
  choice1: {fileID: 1530363298}
  choice2: {fileID: 838602642}
  choice3: {fileID: 314781445}
  background: {fileID: 643133838}
  swap: {fileID: -2564619566193218763, guid: 14868bca79fa65f44affd86bbf8df24e, type: 3}
  typingSpeed: 0.03
  dialogChunks:
  - text: It's time for class... You'll have the option to attend one of three classes
      each day.
    speakerName: Narrator
    portrait: {fileID: 5364273658523971450, guid: c07bf2f52cad3fa4a8befaf3b20f33a7, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: 'Each class will boost one of your three core sheep skills, which may come
      in handy later: "rizz," "aura," and "hax."'
    speakerName: Narrator
    portrait: {fileID: 5364273658523971450, guid: c07bf2f52cad3fa4a8befaf3b20f33a7, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: It's advised to invest heavily into one particular sheep skill, instead
      of being a jack of all trade, master of none.
    speakerName: Narrator
    portrait: {fileID: 5364273658523971450, guid: c07bf2f52cad3fa4a8befaf3b20f33a7, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: So, what am I gonna do today?
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: 
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 1
    choices:
    - How to "BAH"
    - Dodging Arrows 101
    - Picking Locks at Nettlecombe Court
    choiceMaps: 050000000600000007000000
    stat: 720061006800
  - text: Wow, I feel like I've gotten better at effective communication and stand
      out more in sheep society. My "rizz" has gone up!
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: Wow, I feel like I'm a more powerful presence and my physicality has increased.
      My "aura" has gone up!
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: Wow, I feel like I've become more dexterous and my sneaking skills have
      surely improved. My "hax" has gone up!
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: It's a new day, full to the brim with new classes to try out.
    speakerName: Narrator
    portrait: {fileID: 5364273658523971450, guid: c07bf2f52cad3fa4a8befaf3b20f33a7, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: So, what'll I do today?
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: 
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 1
    choices:
    - To be a Sheep in Wolf's Clothing
    - Talking while Eating
    - Bodybuilding (for Sheep)
    choiceMaps: 070000000500000006000000
    stat: 680072006100
  - text: It's hard to believe S-PAIR is halfway done.
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: Well, enough about the future, what class should I go to today?
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: 
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 1
    choices:
    - How to be Bipedal
    - Bull Room Dance
    - Wool Trimming 101
    choiceMaps: 060000000700000005000000
    stat: 610068007200
  - text: It's almost time for de-S-PAIR. Perhaps the skills you learn here could
      help in your final standoff.
    speakerName: Narrator
    portrait: {fileID: 5364273658523971450, guid: c07bf2f52cad3fa4a8befaf3b20f33a7, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: So, where'll I go today?
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: 
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 1
    choices:
    - How to Sheep Talk
    - Barrel Rolling 101
    - Killing Humans for Dummies
    choiceMaps: 050000000700000006000000
    stat: 720068006100
  - text: Today's the day alright.
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: But first, what class should I attend?
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 0
    choices: []
    choiceMaps: 
    stat: 
  - text: 
    speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 6749234275523321579, guid: cf6c107197e5c6143b61ac835d77b2ed, type: 3}
    showChoices: 1
    choices:
    - Is Sheep the One?
    - Offense with the Dark Arts
    - Fluff is Stuff
    choiceMaps: 050000000600000007000000
    stat: 720061006800
  paths: 01000000020000000300000004000000ffffffffffffffffffffffffffffffff090000000a000000ffffffff0c0000000d000000ffffffff0f00000010000000ffffffff1200000013000000ffffffff
